Packaging checklist, in order:

00  Is everything backed up?

01  Make sure we have the right =KT= Bullet
02  Rez =KT= Bullet on ground (not attach)
03  Update "KrakenTech Bullet Script" if needed
04  Make sure script has "Next owner: Modify" unchecked in properties
05  Update/Reset scripts on =KT= Bullet
06  Make sure object has "Next owner: Modify" unchecked in Build Tools->General
07  Makes sure object has "Anyone: Move" checked in Build Tools->General
08  Take updated copy of =KT= Bullet into Inventory if needed

09  Make sure we have the right =KT= Fire Blanket
10  Rez =KT= Fire Blanket on ground (not attach)
11  Update "KrakenTech Fire Blanket Script" if needed
12  Make sure script has "Next owner: Modify" unchecked in properties
13  Delete old =KT= Bullet from =KT= Fire Blanket contents
14  Drag updated and reset =KT= Bullet into =KT= Fire Blanket contents
15  Update/Reset scripts on =KT= Fire Blanket
16  Make sure object has "Next owner: Modify" unchecked in Build Tools->General
17  Take updated copy of =KT= Fire Blanket into Inventory

18  Make sure we have the right =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser
19  Rez =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser on ground (not attach)
20  Update "KrakenTech Fire Blanket Dispenser Script" if needed
21  Make sure script has "Next owner: Modify" unchecked in properties
22  Make sure script is No Modify next owner
23  Delete old =KT= Fire Blanket from =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser contents
24  Drag updated and reset =KT= Fire Blanket into =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser contents
25  Update/Reset scripts on =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser
26  Make sure object has "Next owner: Transfer" unchecked in Build Tools->General
27  Take updated copy of =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser into inventory

28  Rez a new copy of =KT= Fire Blanket Dispenser
29  Do basic tests with it